quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  22,49,"Ini: \"a yimdanen! Nek, $uôwen, d aneddaô kan ipbegginen"
  22,50,"I wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ssmaê akked ôôeéq ukyis"
  22,51,"Wid iaânan asfunneg issekniyen nne£, widak d at ujajiê"
  22,52,"Ur d Nuzen, uqbel ik, amazan ne$ nnbi, mebla ma ikecm ed Cciîan, deg wayen imenna, ma imenna. Itekkes Öebbi ayen d issekcam Cciîan, sinna, Itebbit issekniyen iS. Öebbi d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab"
  22,53,"Iwakken ad Irr aggway n Cciîan d ahewwel, i at wulawen iblan akked at wulawen aquôan. Ih, imednas atnan di t$ennant tu$miqt"
  22,54,"Iwakken ad éôen wid iwumi teppunefk tmusni, ar neppa d tidep, s$uô Mass ik. Ad amnen yis. Ad as anzen wulawen nnsen. Öebbi, s tidep, Inehhu wid iumnen, s abrid uwqim"
  22,55,"Zgan wid ijehlen di ccekk fellas, ar ten id ias yimir, deqzalla, ne$ ibbwev iten id uâaqeb n wass abarar"
  22,56,"Assen, tagelda i Öebbi. Ad Iêudd garasen. Wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ad ilin di Loennet n ssuâada"
  22,57,"I wid ijehlen, iskaddben issekniyen nne£, aâaqeb isdullun"